跨性侮辱性语言</a>后收到了多起死亡威胁。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jess-glynne-reveals-she-nearly-quit-music-due-to-the-scrutiny-3751268">Jess Glynne 的帖子透露，由于“审查”，她几乎放弃了音乐事业，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)、克里斯·马丁 (Chris Martin)、尼罗·罗杰斯 (Nile Rodgers) 等人出现在 Disney+ 系列“卡姆登”的抢先图片中https://www.nme.com/news/tv/dua-lipa-chris-martin-nile-rodgers-and-more-feature-in-first-look-images-of-disney-series-camden-3751275？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=dua-lipa-chris-martin-nile-rodgers-and-first-look-images-of-disney-series-camden 中的更多功能Chris EdwardsFri, 26 Apr 2024 16:32:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3751275 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>即将推出的剧集将探讨一些世界上最伟大的流行歌星如何受到卡姆登的影响而塑造他们的职业生涯</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/dua-lipa-chris-martin-nile-rodgers-and-more-feature-in-first-look-images-of-disney-series-camden-3751275">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)、克里斯·马丁 (Chris Martin)、尼罗·罗杰斯 (Nile Rodgers) 等人出现在 Disney+ 系列“卡姆登”的抢先图片中，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/brands/disney">Disney+</a>公布了即将推出的纪录片系列<em>《卡姆登》</em>的新图片，该系列纪录片将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-martin">克里斯·马丁</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-ronson">马克·罗森</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boy-george">男孩乔治</a>等人主演。</p><p>这部纪录片系列由杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 担任执行制片，将于 5 月在 Disney+ 独家首映，将与世界上一些最知名的音乐明星一起深入幕后，揭示卡姆登如何塑造他们的生活和职业生涯的不为人知的故事。</p><p>今天（4 月 26 日）发布的新照片由 Dua Lipa、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-martin">Coldplay</a>的 Chris Martin、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nile-rodgers">Nile Rodgers</a> 、Boy George 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yungblud">Yungblud</a>主演。确认出演该系列的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines"><em>The Libertines</em></a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">Pete Doherty</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/carl-barat">Carl Barat</a> 、Mark Ronson、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/questlove">Questlove</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-eyed-peas">Black Eyed Peas</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soul-ii-soul">Soul II Soul</a>的 Jazzie B、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chuck-d">Chuck D</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/faithless">Faithless</a>的 Sister Bliss。</p><p>即将上映的剧集由 Lightbox 制作，Lightbox 是由奥斯卡获奖制片人西蒙·钦 (Simon Chinn) 和艾美奖获奖制片人乔纳森·钦 (Jonathan Chinn) 创立的制作公司，与 Day One Pictures 联合制作，Day One Pictures 是由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse</a> ) 的原经纪人尼克·希曼斯基 (Nick Shymansky) 共同创立的制作公司和激进22。</p><p>阿西夫·卡帕迪亚 (Asif Kapadia) 担任剧集导演，单集将由托比·特克曼 (Toby Trackman)、耶米·巴米罗 (Yemi Bamiro) 和莎拉·兰伯特 (Sarah Lambert) 执导。</p><p>看看下面的“卡姆登”的第一眼图片。 </p><figure id="attachment_3751288" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3751288" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3751288" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dua-Lipa-in-Camden.jpeg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dua-Lipa-in-Camden.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dua-Lipa-in-Camden-400x254.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dua-Lipa-in-Camden-800x508.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dua-Lipa-in-Camden-696x442.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dua-Lipa-in-Camden-1392x884.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dua-Lipa-in-Camden-1068x678.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3751288" class="wp-caption-text"> Dua Lipa 担任迪士尼+新剧集“卡姆登”的执行制片人。图片来源：迪士尼</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3751290" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3751290" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3751290" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chris-Martin-in-the-Dua-Lipa-produced-Disney-series-Camden.jpeg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chris-Martin-in-the-Dua-Lipa-produced-Disney-serie